      <title>克什米尔即将举行投票，印度得票率已过半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/india-election-crosses-halfway-mark-with-focus-on-low-turnout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[位于动荡的查谟和克什米尔地区的一座城市斯利那加周一在印度第四阶段全国选举中进行了投票，人们对选民投票率低下和竞选活动日益激烈的担忧日益加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/india-election-crosses-halfway-mark-with-focus-on-low-turnout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克试图通过恐惧来减缓斯塔默向英国大选胜利迈进的步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/sunak-attempts-to-re-frame-uk-election-with-focus-on-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 表示，在工党政府领导下，英国将变得不那么安全，他敦促选民不要看他所在的保守党在任 14 年来的记录，他承认这些记录并不“完美”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-12/sunak-attempts-to-re-frame-uk-election-with-focus-on-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
